sql:
SELECT COUNT(*) AS approved_comments_count
FROM holiday_comments
WHERE holiday_id = 1 AND is_approved = 1;

SELECT holiday_name
FROM holidays
ORDER BY holiday_name;

external_knowledge:
External knowledge:
- Holidays are special days of celebration or commemoration; 
- The year 2023 is the one being considered for this query.

sql:
SELECT COUNT(*) AS holiday_count
FROM holidays
WHERE year = 2023;

SELECT type_name, description
FROM holiday_types
ORDER BY type_name ASC;
